## Project Structure & Modules

The codebase is a **Maven multi-module reactor** with **14 modules**:

| Layer | Module | Purpose |
|-------|--------|---------|
| **Foundation** | [shared-kernel](file:///e:/CoAgent4U/shared-kernel) | Pure Java value objects — `UserId`, [AgentId](file:///e:/CoAgent4U/shared-kernel/src/main/java/com/coagent4u/shared/AgentId.java#9-28), `CoordinationId`, [TimeSlot](file:///e:/CoAgent4U/shared-kernel/src/main/java/com/coagent4u/shared/TimeSlot.java#10-28), `Email`, etc. Zero dependencies. |
| **Foundation** | [common-domain](file:///e:/CoAgent4U/common-domain) | [DomainEvent](file:///e:/CoAgent4U/common-domain/src/main/java/com/coagent4u/common/DomainEvent.java#11-23) interface + published event types (`UserRegistered`, [CoordinationCompleted](file:///e:/CoAgent4U/common-domain/src/main/java/com/coagent4u/common/event/CoordinationCompleted.java#13-23), `ApprovalDecisionMade`, etc.) |
| **Core** | [user-module](file:///e:/CoAgent4U/core/user-module) | User aggregate, Slack identity, service connections. Ports: `RegisterUserUseCase`, `UserPersistencePort`, etc. |
| **Core** | [agent-module](file:///e:/CoAgent4U/core/agent-module) | Agent aggregate, `IntentParser` (rule-based), `ConflictDetector`. Inbound: `HandleMessageUseCase`, `ViewScheduleUseCase`. Outbound: `CalendarPort`, `LLMPort`, `ApprovalPort`. Also implements coordination capability ports. |
| **Core** | [coordination-module](file:///e:/CoAgent4U/core/coordination-module) | Coordination aggregate, 14-state state machine, `AvailabilityMatcher`, `ProposalGenerator`, `EventCreationSaga`. |
| **Core** | [approval-module](file:///e:/CoAgent4U/core/approval-module) | Approval aggregate with status tracking and expiration policy. |
| **Integration** | [calendar-module](file:///e:/CoAgent4U/integration/calendar-module) | `GoogleCalendarAdapter` — implements `CalendarPort` for Google Calendar API. |
| **Integration** | [messaging-module](file:///e:/CoAgent4U/integration/messaging-module) | `SlackInboundAdapter` (webhook handler) + `SlackNotificationAdapter` (outbound notifications). |
| **Integration** | [llm-module](file:///e:/CoAgent4U/integration/llm-module) | `GroqLLMAdapter` — implements `LLMPort` for Groq cloud API (intent parsing fallback + schedule summary). |
| **Infra** | [persistence](file:///e:/CoAgent4U/infrastructure/persistence) | JPA entities, mappers, Spring Data repositories implementing all `PersistencePort` interfaces. Houses Flyway migrations. |
| **Infra** | [security](file:///e:/CoAgent4U/infrastructure/security) | JWT validation/issuing, AES-256-GCM token encryption, Slack signature verification, rate limiting. |
| **Infra** | [config](file:///e:/CoAgent4U/infrastructure/config) | `application.yml` profiles (dev, prod). |
| **Infra** | [monitoring](file:///e:/CoAgent4U/infrastructure/monitoring) | `SpringEventPublisherAdapter` (implements `DomainEventPublisher`), audit logging, metrics. |
| **Assembly** | [coagent-app](file:///e:/CoAgent4U/coagent-app) | Spring Boot entry point — wires all modules together via component scanning. |

