## Tech Stack

| Category | Technology |
|----------|------------|
| Language | Java 21 (records, sealed classes) |
| Framework | Spring Boot 3.4.3 |
| Database | PostgreSQL 15 (NeonDB remote or local Docker) |
| Migrations | Flyway |
| ORM | Spring Data JPA / Hibernate |
| Messaging | Slack SDK (webhooks + Block Kit) |
| Calendar | Google Calendar API |
| LLM | Groq API (Tier 2 intent parsing fallback) |
| Security | JWT (HS256), AES-256-GCM, Slack HMAC-SHA256 |
| Testing | JUnit 5, Mockito, Testcontainers, WireMock, ArchUnit |
| Build | Maven 3.9+, Docker multi-stage |
| Monitoring | Micrometer, structured JSON logging |

